WEBVTT

00:00:00.980 --> 00:00:07.420
Even if the waves of life

00:00:08.940 --> 00:00:18.620
reach deep into the sea,

00:00:18.620 --> 00:00:37.560
In the 잠中,

00:00:37.560 --> 00:00:45.640
Nozoye no koya no himi mo

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:51.600
otori shito wa shirasaru ka

00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:55.800
shuuni somu kazoya ni tsukai e

00:00:55.800 --> 00:01:02.200
zin ni juu ko no ni te sae tatawa

00:01:02.520 --> 00:01:07.160
mosohan no jirima imo

00:01:07.160 --> 00:01:11.720
hyakuman no kun ni

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:17.160
natsu masaru yo

00:01:24.160 --> 00:01:30.960
Oya, onore ga kokoro tada hitotsu de

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:36.000
shirushi wa mokusen kore o mi yo

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:40.240
mononofu no inochi wo sa

00:01:40.240 --> 00:01:44.640
otsu wo yaiba mo

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:49.040
oi ni kono yo na

00:01:49.040 --> 00:01:53.040
shishito ni dake no

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:57.440
shishitsuki yari

00:01:58.440 --> 00:02:07.440
shu wo koroshita

00:02:07.440 --> 00:02:18.440
tenbatsu no mukui wa

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:24.440
koya ni mo

00:02:24.440 --> 00:02:28.440
kano otori to

00:02:28.440 --> 00:02:33.440
yari no osaki ni te wo kakete

00:02:33.440 --> 00:02:38.440
ien ni

00:02:38.440 --> 00:02:47.440
iku shi mo

00:02:47.440 --> 00:02:54.440
ki yo mo ki yo

